*Veoma* je hladno danas. (It is very cold today.)

*Veoma* sam siguran da će moje rešenje raditi. (I am very sure that my solution will work.)

*Veoma* se trudim da budem bolji čovek. (I am trying very hard to be a better person.)

*Veoma* sam zahvalan što mi je pomogla. (I am very grateful that she helped me.)

*Veoma* mi je drago što je uspeo. (I am very glad that he succeeded.)

*Veoma* sam zabrinut zbog njega. (I am very worried about him.)